{"tid":1579330,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀緊教大part time  degree好辛苦","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:31:42.000Z","uid":323832,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8723abf56fb015dd4b019d496472bf3a9d859713","tid":1579330,"uid":323832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"我係一位90後幼稚園老師，讀緊特教part time degree.<br />\n<br />\n基本上，人地放工，我就要番工。<br />\n<br />\n番左3星期，有種好趕頭趕命，兼累到爆既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n尤其是住屯天元果D（我就係），我一定要910-915左右要走，否則趕唔到果架去天水圍校巴，兼要轉好多次先番到天水圍。<br />\n<br />\n我計過，番三日學，車費＋食野，都洗左我2000蚊<br />\n<br />\n唉！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n仲有兩年要捱，淨係e家我都覺得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2297263b47929d8f86386926a010c9980378065c","tid":1579330,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"每日洗六百幾蚊？<br />\n當你車費$150(應該已經計多咗俾你)<br />\n你都唔會每餐食百幾$200啦？"},{"pid":"0f407fda8969370631a9b44019210b4279c68dd6","tid":1579330,"uid":323832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2297263b47929d8f86386926a010c9980378065c","tid":1579330,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"每日洗六百幾蚊？<br />\n當你車費$150(應該已經計多咗俾你)<br />\n你都唔會每餐食百幾$200啦？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"Sor，計錯左，係500幾蚊"},{"pid":"6484bd79bc248413c59363d4df2a5a5c46fe378b","tid":1579330,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"我都想讀呀，我想問interview 難唔難？ 同埋要gpa 幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />